Introduction

Kim Minsol is a South Korean trainee.

She mostly gained recognisation for her participation in MBC's survival show My Teenage Girl in 2021, and Mnet's survival show I-LAND2: N/a in 2024. Sadly, she got eliminated from both survival shows and was unable to make her debut.
